agnet and validate the band crossing with concurrent measurements\nof topological invariant in a continuously tuned topological phase transition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Nov 2020 16:44:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-07"}
