tic and fluid simulations\nshow consistency for the macroscopic properties and transport fluxes between\nboth regimes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Nov 2020 17:24:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Nov 2020 14:22:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-15"}
