 the 0.18um time-based RDC with\nspeed-up latch offers the highest resolution. The active chip-area for all\n3-designs are less than 1.1 mm^2.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Nov 2020 23:48:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-03"}
