and\n(relative short advance planning horizons) operations can offer many benefits\nfor all stakeholders involved (passengers, operators, and cities).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Nov 2020 08:43:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-03"}
