hes. By complementing 3D printing with finite\nelement analysis topology optimization we can simulate a specific optimum shape\nfor the given input parameters and external boundary conditions. The next set\nof prototypes is designed taking to account the calculation of topology\noptimisation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Nov 2020 14:20:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-03"}
